snippet.textDisplay:
Music is ethereal. It is beyond language, culture, emotions and is even enjoyed by other species. It can be influenced by the same things it is not bound by because it is enjoyed and appreciated by people alien to those influences. 
India is a country of innumerable cultures, which blesses us with various tunes and melodies. I find Rajasthani music to be an embodiment of raw emotions, as exemplified in this music video. If you notice, the creation of this masterpiece is accomplished by musicians and musical instruments from across the globe.

snippet.textDisplay:
Everytime I feel like giving up on Indian classical music, I am pleasantly surprised by a gem like this one 👌👌👌👌👌 I have been consistently listening to this one on loop for the past one week and still I find it new each time 👍👍👍👍

Hai 08 saal puraana gaana but phir bhi aaj ke gaanon ko paani pilaa de. Very rustic, very Indian, very melodious & very very soulful indeed.

Superb in every aspect and easily in my top 50 Indian songs of all time 👍👍👍👍👍👍👍👍👍👍
